---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Contact" description="Entrer en contact avec Bonarchi SIMEU.">
  <article class="wrap prose">
    <span class="ledger-no">00</span>
    <h1>Contact</h1>
    <p class="lede">
      Le plus rapide pour me joindre, c'est le courriel. Je lis tout ; je réponds à presque tout.
    </p>

    <ul class="contact-list">
      <li>
        <span class="meta">Courriel</span>
        <a href="mailto:bonarchisimeu@gmail.com">bonarchisimeu@gmail.com</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="meta">LinkedIn</span>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/bonarchisimeu">linkedin.com/in/bonarchisimeu</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="meta">GitHub</span>
        <a href="https://github.com/bonarchisimeu">github.com/bonarchisimeu</a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  .prose { padding-top: 2.5rem; max-width: 44rem; }
  .lede { font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--ink-soft); }
  .contact-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  .contact-list li { display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 1rem; padding: 0.75rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }
  .contact-list .meta { min-width: 6rem; }
  .contact-list a { font-size: 1.1rem; }
</style>
